original_title: Influenceurs : une vie de rêve à Dubaï
overview: Influencers are Instagram users who have an established credibility and audience; who can persuade others by virtue of their trustworthiness and authenticity but what are these influencers lives really like? Is it different from what they show on social media?
tagline: Learn the truth about their perfect life!
title: Influenceurs : une vie de rêve à Dubaï
